{"id": 2409, "genre": 1004, "title": "在“拒绝别人”这件事上，你是哪一型人格？来测！", "description": "关于如何说不，看看你的表现更接近于谁。（题图来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images）", "record_count": 28438, "comment_count": 137, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180610213629hds4BeZA7uC29rnt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 6, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-22T17:00:00Z", "column": null, "normal_questions": [{"id": 4395, "content": "亲戚突然打电话说“到了你的城市，一起吃晚饭”，你更可能说：", "image": "img/question/question/201806190944185GWfFRhnwDY6U2Sd.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287873, "title": "“有安排了，以后早点通知”", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287874, "title": "“要加班，不好意思”", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287875, "title": "“在外地，赶不回来”", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287876, "title": "“好的，到时候见”", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4397, "content": "好朋友说要借宿你家，但你并不习惯和人同处一室，你更可能说：", "image": "img/question/question/20180619094442mveXlF6P5S0IEUxY.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287877, "title": "“不太方便，你再问问其他人”", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287878, "title": "“我最近也不在家呢”", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287879, "title": "“帮你订个旅店吧这样住得舒服点”", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287880, "title": "“啊……行……”", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4398, "content": "假如被拒绝借宿的这位朋友之后请求“通融一下”，你更可能：", "image": "img/question/question/20180619094500vZ37rcu5xpMXeG2U.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287882, "title": "心里更加反感，“我都已经说过不行了”", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287883, "title": "不为所动、内心毫无波澜", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287884, "title": "商量一下具体条件，比如借宿时的作息时间", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287885, "title": "很容易心软，“那好吧”", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4399, "content": "朋友想借对你来说不算小的一笔钱，拒绝后你的感受更接近：", "image": "img/question/question/20180619094520bSxnrciaYKf51tTX.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287886, "title": "感到有点内疚", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287887, "title": "觉得无所谓", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287889, "title": "内心怪朋友提这种尴尬的要求", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287890, "title": "能借就借，不太可能拒绝", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4400, "content": "同事一直找你帮忙做职责之外的小事，你更可能：", "image": "img/question/question/20180619094539xypIA7gZloX160Qc.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287891, "title": "直接告诉 ta “这不是我的事，以后别找我了”", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287892, "title": "请老板或主管帮忙沟通一下", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287893, "title": "每次都找“我太忙了”之类的理由推脱", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287894, "title": "时间允许就默默做了", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4401, "content": "不太熟的同学在微信上发来同城婚礼邀约，你更可能：", "image": "img/question/question/20180619094554Ltps8aDSEVZrzx9o.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287896, "title": "干脆不理，当没看见", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287898, "title": "推脱有事，也不会给红包", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287900, "title": "不去，但会找人带红包", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287903, "title": "有空还是会去", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4402, "content": "被热情的亲戚介绍对象但不想去，这种情况下你更可能：", "image": "img/question/question/201806190946147qEQoY5MyIXw9axP.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287912, "title": "直接说“不喜欢相亲”“不急着找对象”", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287913, "title": "找个理由“已经有人在交往了”", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287914, "title": "先答应下来，每次对方要见的时候推脱有事", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287916, "title": "觉得“还是得去认识一下”", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4403, "content": "和爸妈的朋友吃饭被问“工资多少”，不想回答的你通常会：", "image": "img/question/question/20180619094634gKwIfjl5YA0pVyxB.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287918, "title": "“哎呀这是个人隐私”", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287920, "title": "瞎编一个数，赶紧换个话题", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287921, "title": "反应不过来，一般就实话实说了", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287919, "title": "“没多少没多少”", "score": 1.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4404, "content": "收到一个 offer 但觉得工资太低不想去，你更有可能：", "image": "img/question/question/20180619094659z2kvfJyItHLAoEDR.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287922, "title": "直接提出工资不符合要求", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287924, "title": "委婉告知自己有其他安排", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287925, "title": "提出考虑一周，晚点拒绝", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287926, "title": "拖到快入职的时候才决定", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4405, "content": "在各种“不好拒绝别人”的时候，你的内心 os 更多是：", "image": "img/question/question/20180619094717im0HXFutE3zNGgpL.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 287928, "title": "关系搞坏了，下次还怎么找 ta 帮忙", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287931, "title": "唉，不好意思开口", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287929, "title": "不知道怎么圆谎，说漏了咋办", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 287932, "title": "没什么不好意思的，该说不就说不", "score": 3.0, "image": null}]}]}